    <title>Simplicial resolutions for the second power of square-free monomial
  ideals</title>
    <summary>  Given a square-free monomial ideal $I$, we define a simplicial complex
labeled by the generators of $I^2$ which supports a free resolution of $I^2$.
As a consequence, we obtain (sharp) upper bounds on the Betti numbers of the
second power of any square-free monomial ideal.
</summary>
